snippet.title: Oversampled
snippet.description:
Oversampled is helping out producers by bringing quality sounds, music production tutorials and fresh inspirations.

Never enough samples to get oversampled.
Oversampled - you can say your project is oversampled when there is no more space for samples.

If you want to talk to me, ask me some questions or just be friends :)
https://instagram.com/oversampled.us


My studio equipment:
*Audio interface: NI Komplete Audio 6
*DAW: Ableton Live 10 Suite
*Headphones: Bayerdynamic DT1990 Pro 250Ohm
*Monitors: Yamaha HS8
*Mic: Audio-Technica AT2020
*MIDI Controller: Komplete Kontrol S88 MKII

PC Specs:
*OS: Windows 10
*CPU: AMD Ryzen 9 3900X 12-Core 3.80 GHz
*RAM: 32GB
*GPU: Nvidia RTX 2070 Super
*SSD: 1TB (3500 MB/s R/W)

My Ableton theme: https://www.livethemes.co/themes/yello-by-live-themes-remixed/28636
My Serum skin: https://www.defrocksounds.com/product/deluxerock-basic/
